<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <title>AI Image Challenge - Arena</title>
    <%- include('partials/head') %>
    <style>
        .challenge-item {
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
        }
        .challenge-item:hover {
            transform: scale(1.02);
            box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
        }
        .challenge-overlay {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            background: linear-gradient(transparent, rgba(0,0,0,0.9));
            padding: 2rem;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-dark text-light">
    <%- include('partials/nav') %>

    <div class="container py-5">
        <div class="text-center mb-5">
            <h1 class="display-4 fw-bold text-info mb-3">🔥 ARENA CHALLENGES</h1>
            <p class="text-secondary lead">이미지 속 숨겨진 프롬프트를 맞추고 랭킹에 도전하세요!</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Arena Notice -->
        <div class="arena-notice p-4 rounded-4 text-center mb-5 fade-in">
            <p class="mb-0 text-secondary small">
                모든 이미지는 AI로 생성되었습니다. 도전하고 싶은 챌린지를 선택하세요. <br>
                이미지 생성이 처음이라면 <a href="https://arena.ai" target="_blank" class="text-info text-decoration-underline fw-bold">arena.ai</a>에서 시작해보세요.
            </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Challenge Grid -->
        <div class="row g-4">
            <% if (challenges && challenges.length > 0) { %>
                <% challenges.forEach(c => { %>
                    <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
                        <div class="challenge-card challenge-item h-100 position-relative" onclick="location.href='/challenge/<%= c.id %>'">
                            <img src="/api/image/<%= c.result_image %>" class="card-img-top" style="height: 300px; object-fit: cover;" alt="Challenge">
                            <div class="challenge-overlay">
                                <h3 class="h5 fw-bold text-white mb-1">Challenge #<%= c.id %></h3>
                                <p class="small text-info mb-0">진행 중 &middot; <%= c.start_date %> ~ <%= c.end_date %></p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                <% }) %>
            <% } else { %>
                <div class="col-12 text-center py-5">
                    <p class="text-secondary">현재 진행 중인 챌린지가 없습니다.</p>
                </div>
            <% } %>
        </div>
    </div>

    <%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>
